The paper focuses on image captioning, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of contextual information from news articles also suggests a potential fit for information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the proposed model involves the dynamic extension of the output dictionary, which is a technique commonly used in natural language generation and could be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
